does it work?
ive already downloaded this by thethingy and activator wont work, cant really waste anymore of my life trying, need a guaranteed working version before i can download and seed it
Yes it works I have it installed now. Its BIE. So it WILL always work.

On the image is a folder called "BIE"

There are 2 cracks. If the 1 doesn't work the other one WILL work.

Thanks cavedog2, works great. First time thought that activator doesn't work, because it failed many times, until I ran it as Administrator.
http://i.servut.us/i/bie_working.png


Installation:
--------------
1. Burn Image to DVD
2. Boot from DVD / USB
3. Install to unpartitioned space without serial
3. Check BIE-Dir on DVD
4. Start bie_7install64.exe (MUST RUN AS ADMIN, or it fails)
5. Enjoy!
